jpredapir: A package for interfacing with JPred server.

Source: R/jpredapir.R
jpredapir.Rd

The jpredapir package provides functions to submit, check status, and retrieve results from JPred: A Secondary Structure Prediction Server (JPred).

Details

This package contains a collection of functions to interface with JPred server.

For a complete list, use library(help = "jpredapir").

The jpredapir package functions

  • jpredapir::submit() Submit job to JPred REST interface.

  • jpredapir::status() Check job status on JPred REST interface.

  • jpredapir::get_results() Download results from JPred server.

  • jpredapir::quota() Check JPred REST interface quota.

  • jpredapir::check_rest_version() Check version of JPred REST interface.
